<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued January 06 at 5:52PM EST until January 07 at 4:00AM EST by NWS Buffalo</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 AM EST
SUNDAY...
* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of 1 to 2 inches.
* WHERE...Allegany county.
* WHEN...Until 4 AM EST Sunday.
* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions.</description>
<instruction>Periods of snow will result in snow covered roads and limited
visibilities. Slow down and use caution while driving.
Submit snow reports through our website or social media.</instruction>
